# OpenCode talks to MANY providers and only reads project/global opencode.json
# (not OPENCODE_CONFIG). We MERGE a forwarding baseURL into EACH provider the user
# uses, encoding that provider's REAL endpoint, so the proxy forwards every
# provider correctly with NO pinned upstream — full freedom of provider/model.
